product_description: Granola bars are a convenient and portable snack made from a mixture of rolled oats, nuts, seeds, and sweeteners like honey or maple syrup.
Greek yogurt is a thick and creamy dairy product made by straining regular yogurt to remove excess whey.
Salmon fillets are portions of salmon, a popular fatty fish rich in omega-3 fatty acids.
Avocado oil is a cooking oil extracted from the pulp of ripe avocados.
Quinoa salad kits are pre-packaged meal solutions that typically include cooked and seasoned quinoa, along with a variety of fresh vegetables, herbs, and dressing.
